Package: markov3d
Type: Package
Title: Markov process model to analyze 3D genome data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yinan Wang
Maintainer: Yinan Wang <yinan.wang@pku.edu.cn>
Description: Model the dynamic interactions between protein and genome by Markov
    process. The model computes the steady-state distribution of proteins on the
    genome. See <publication> for details.
